    <span class="cs-card-title">Show the work, not the need</span>
    <span class="cs-card-body">A visual and editorial direction built around GOAL's impact on the ground, not humanitarian suffering.</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cs-card-block">
    <span class="cs-card-num">002</span>
    <span class="cs-card-title">Four pillars, total clarity</span>
    <span class="cs-card-body">A navigation architecture that simplified a complex organisation into an immediately legible structure for any visitor.</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cs-card-block">
    <span class="cs-card-num">003</span>
    <span class="cs-card-title">Built for the team, not just the user</span>
    <span class="cs-card-body">A CMS and campaign page framework that gave GOAL's comms and fundraising teams the autonomy to publish and react without technical dependency.</span>
  </div>
</div>

